    "multiple_images_with_text_f6mjKX": {
      "type": "multiple-images-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "item_LxJKVU": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "image_rotation_degrees": -2,
            "subheading": "Body is in the course of dynamic movement. You change posture every day, even though you sit on a chair.",
            "title": "Advanced industry technology",
            "heading_tag": "h4",
            "content": "<p>Adaptive adjustable massage lumbar support. AutoFull's ingenious lumbar support system is structured in a way whether you lean back or forward, it fits your back - the chair moves and supports your body as desired. Over the past 4 years, we studied dozens of lumbar support structures, conceived of more than a hundred designs in terms of structure or materials, fabricated and sampled over 20 prototypes, and made constant refinement.<br/>In the end, we abandoned the conventional timber support, and figured out the best combination - PA+GF and toughened PP+GF through trial and error. The lumbar support ensures comfort and durable support, while featuring a certain amount of elasticity, Besides, we have researched on over 100 back curves of sub- jects that vary by body shapes, analyzed back pressure distri- bution of subjects at different sitting positions using millime- ter-level pressure acquisition instrument, ultimately drawing the most ideal back design curve. The carefully designed hyperbolic curve makes lumbar sup- port better fit back curve. You get the best lumbar support no matter where you are and how you sit.</p>",
            "button_url": "",
            "button_text": ""
          }
        },
        "item_YhrjLi": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "image_rotation_degrees": 1.5,
            "subheading": "We give a pledge on the use of the top-tier elastics in the industry.",
            "title": "Premium industry technology High polymer elastics",
            "heading_tag": "h4",
            "content": "<p>Our advanced high-pressure foaming equipment allows us to develop high polymer elastics for the internal support of our gaming chairs, seamlessly combining incredible softness with superior support, albeit at a higher price point.</p>",
            "button_url": "",
            "button_text": ""
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "item_LxJKVU",
        "item_YhrjLi"
      ],
      "disabled": true,
      "settings": {
