        "subheading": "",
        "title": "HVAC seat cushion",
        "content": "<p>For cozier user experience, the AutoFull M6 Ultra is equipped with HVAC functionality for both ventilation and heating. Each feature has three gears to ensure ultimate experience of users.</p>",
        "background": "",
        "background_gradient": "",
