          "settings": {
            "image_rotation_degrees": -2,
            "subheading": "Our self-developed armrest gives stable support to arms at all angles, helping mitigate arm and shoulder strain in consequence of prolonged use of PC.",
            "title": "360° omnidirectional armrests",
            "heading_tag": "h4",
            "content": "<p>The 360° omnidirectional armrest offers users with greater flexibility and adaptability and satisfies users' demands in different usage scenarios. It enhances users' performance in working, gaming and learning. When using PC for long periods, the armrest can support your arms and elbows, preventing discomfort resulting from sus- pension or improper support. Assured arm and shoulder comfort helps relieve arm and shoulder strain attributable to prolonged use of PC. Offer strong arm support in all usage scenarios.</p>",
